{
  "title": "Indulgent Venezuelan Sweet Red Pepper Ceviche",
  "description": "A salty, light, and indulgent Venezuelan dish featuring sweet red peppers and bonito shave, sugar-free-friendly and served in a scallop shell.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
